original_title: Chick Corea: The Ultimate Adventure Live In Barcelona 2007
overview: An NEA Jazz Master, 16-time Grammy winner, prolific composer and undisputed keyboard virtuoso, Chick Corea has attained living legend status after four decades of unparalleled creativity and an artistic output that is simply staggering.
title: Chick Corea: The Ultimate Adventure Live In Barcelona 2007
